          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1694182478254-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>fresh</strong> <strong>orecchiette</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled</strong> <strong>water</strong> with a large pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the <strong>orecchiette </strong>for 4-6 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>orecchiette</strong>, reserving a cup of the <strong>starchy</strong> <strong>pasta</strong> <strong>water</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1694182484163-x200.jpg",
