    {
      "instruction": "<p>Tear <strong>half </strong>of your <strong>basil leaves </strong>(save the rest for garnish!) into the pan along with the <strong>chicken stock </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>'Nduja & cherry tomato sauce</strong></p>",
